title: Ep 278 - Jethalal Asks Babita To Teach Him Swimming
shortDesc: Jethalal, eager to learn swimming, visits Babita's house and asks her if he can learn swimming. But is there a twist? Will Jethalal be disappointed?

title: Ep 279 - Ladies Have Fun At The Swimming Club
shortDesc: All the women from Gokuldham society gather at the Silver Club to learn swimming. Meanwhile, Jetha decides to learn swimming from Babita at any cost. What happens next? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 280 - Men Want To Swim Too!
shortDesc: The men also want to learn swimming and want to learn it along with the women. But, they come up with an idea to go swimming along with their family. They take suggestions from Taarak Mehta. Will the men be content with the decision?

title: Ep 281 - Jethalal As A Sardar
shortDesc: Jethalal somehow finds a friend at the club and sneaks in as a waiter. He not only sneaks in, he sneaks in as a Sardar. But, he is shocked and frightened by the female guard at the pool. Watch this episode to find out what happens next.

title: Ep 282 - Jethalal Saves The Day
shortDesc: The entire Gokuldham Society meets at the Club which startles Jethalal.  While Jetha decides to change and join the gang, he notices a man clicking pictures of women in the pool. What will Jethalal do next?

title: Ep 283 - Champak Intervenes Jethalals Romantic Mood
shortDesc: Jethalal is in a romantic mood. He is expressing his love for his wife Daya, asking her for a heads massage. but, Champaklal, the senior member of the house is interfering their lovely mood. Will Jethalal ignore him or burst out at him?

title: Ep 284 - Jethalal Gets Robbed
shortDesc: When Sundar asks for money, Jethalal leaves his house to give him money. On the way, he meets a stranger who asks him for the police station. When Jethalal starts to answer, he points a knife at Jetha and threatens to kill him. What happens next?

title: Ep 285 - Tappus Last Examination.
shortDesc: It is Tappu's last examination and he is well prepared. His family wishes him good luck before sending him to the school. Will their blessings be upon him? Will Tappu successfully complete the exam? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 286 - Goli Wants A Vacation
shortDesc: Now that the exams are over, Goli wants a vacation. But, Hans being a doctor, says that he cannot close his clinic for a long time. How will Goli react? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 287 - Operation Christmas Celebration
shortDesc: The elders of Gokuldham gather around to surprise Tappu Sena for Christmas. the men go for Christmas shopping at a mall. Will the kids be surprised? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 288 - Guess The Santa
shortDesc: As a surprise to the kids, the elders of Gokuldham Society plan on a big Christmas celebration. They all dress up as Santa Claus and ask the kids to guess who their parents are. Tappu then comes up with a great idea. Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 289 - Nattu Kaka Dances At Gada Electronics
shortDesc: Jethalal comes to his shop in the morning to witness Nattu Kaka dance. When asked why he says he was checking the stereo as they'd received a complaint. Later, Jethalal tries to get New Year's Party Passes.

title: Ep 290 - The Party Only For Men
shortDesc: Jethalal gets passes for New Year's and all the men decide to go to the party without their family. Will the wives agree? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 291 - Sundar Tears Jethas Party Passes
shortDesc: Jethalal is excited about the party for New Year's Eve and talks to Sodhi about it. Just then, Sundar comes to the shop and asks him if he wants passes for a different party. He then breaks Jetha's heart by tearing the passes. What happens next?

title: Ep 292 - Sundars Party
shortDesc: Daya assumes that Jethalal and Sundar will and get into a fight because of Sundar's mischief. Later, everyone celebrates New Year's Eve at the society.
